# @pulse/shared-types

Single source of truth for schemas consumed by API, workers, and frontends.

## Export these

- `Mood`: `'high' | 'medium' | 'low' | 'neutral'`
- `TaskStatus`: `'todo' | 'in_progress' | 'review' | 'done'`
- `EventType`: `'created' | 'status_changed' | 'commented' | 'reassigned'`
- `Role`: `'pulse-admin' | 'pulse-member' | 'pulse-viewer'`
- `TaskEvent` — canonical job payload for BullMQ workers
- DTOs for API request/response shapes
- Constants: decay rates, health thresholds, queue names

## TaskEvent shape (workers read this)

```typescript
interface TaskEvent {
  id: string;
  taskId: string;
  actorId: string;
  eventType: EventType;
  oldValue?: string;
  newValue?: string;
  commentText?: string;
  mood: Mood;
  occurredAt: string; // ISO 8601
}
```

## Rules

- No runtime dependencies — types + constants only
- Match `infra/postgres/init.sql` CHECK constraints exactly
- When schema changes, update init.sql and this package together
